verbose_text: Rh heterozygous for the TFP allele of TRIM5alpha and TRIMCyp suppressed viral infection of both SIVsmE543 and SIVsm660 more efficiently than Rh homozygous for either TRIMCyp or TRIM5alpha.
evidence: TRIM5alpha and TRIMCyp suppressed viral infection of both SIVsmE543                                and SIVsm660
